    q: `Two parallel trains run north-south. Train A moves north at $54 \\text{ km/h}$ ($15 \\text{ m/s}$) and Train B moves south at $90 \\text{ km/h}$ ($25 \\text{ m/s}$). What is the relative velocity of B with respect to A?`,
