    correct: 1,
    explanation: `$R = v_x \\times T = v_0\\cos\\theta \\times \\left(\\frac{2v_0\\sin\\theta}{g}\\right) = \\frac{v_0^2(2\\sin\\theta\\cos\\theta)}{g} = \\frac{v_0^2\\sin 2\\theta}{g}$.`
