    q: `A car of mass $1000 \\text{ kg}$ moves at $72 \\text{ km/h}$ on a level road. The engine is switched off. The coefficient of kinetic friction is $0.4$ ($g = 10 \\text{ m/s}^2$). Find the shortest stopping distance.`,
